TextEng: Might I ask your name, friend?
May I ask you some questions?
Who are you?
I would ask a question of you.
Tell me who you are.
Yeah, whatever. I have a question.
Who you?
Me have questions.
Goodbye.
I am called <FirstName>.
My name is <FullName>. Pleased to meet you.
You don't need to know who I am.
Text: 넌 내가 누군지 알 필요 없어.

TextEng: Me is <FirstName>.
Me called <FullName>. Is nice to meet you.
You no need know me.
Text: 너 내 이름 알 필요 없어.

TextEng: What's so terrible about today?
Do you know of any work around here?
Can you tell me what's going on in Luskan?
Text: 러스칸에서 무슨 일이 벌어지고 있는지 말해 줄래?

TextEng: I need some directions.
You tells me what go on in Luskan?
Me looks for work.
Me needs directions.
What bad about today?
Perhaps you could tell me who you are?
Text: 혹시 누군지 말해 줄 수 있나?

TextEng: Who you?
What do you mean?
Why is Kurth holding her captive?
Text: 커스는 왜 그녀를 가둬 둔 거지?

TextEng: Where is she being held? Do you know?
What would the reward be if I rescued her?
I could rescue her for you.
Sorry, but I'm not interested.
Why sister captive?
You knows where she held?
What reward for rescue, maybe?
Me could rescues her.
Nope. Me have no interest. Too busy.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I'm sure I can get your sister back safely.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 네 여동생을 안전하게 데려올 수 있어.

TextEng: Fine, if you don't want my help, so be it.
Text: 좋아, 내 도움이 필요 없다면 그러라지.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me get sister back safe, no problem.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 누이 안전하게 데려와, 문제 없어.

TextEng: Fine, me go then.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> All right... but don't you think some coin up front might be suitable for my trouble?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 좋아... 하지만 수고비로 선금 좀 주는 게 맞지 않겠어?

TextEng: Fine. But I want some coin now. Cough it up before I search your corpse.
Text: 좋아. 하지만 지금 당장 돈을 내. 안 그러면 시체에서 뒤져 가질 테니까.

TextEng: I'll do what I can.
Text: 할 수 있는 만큼 해 보지.

TextEng: Evaine will be returned safe and sound, I promise.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me think some coin now be good idea, no?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 생각해 지금 돈 좀 주는 게 좋아, 안 그래?

TextEng: You give me coin now. And me means now, or else me get angry.
Text: 지금 돈 줘. 지금이야. 아니면 나 화낸다.

TextEng: Me do that.
Evaine come back safe, me promise.
Tell me again how to find her?
Text: 다시 그녀를 어떻게 찾는지 말해 줄래?

TextEng: I found Evaine in Kurth's fortress, but she isn't with me at the moment.
Text: 커스의 요새에서 에바인을 찾았지만, 지금은 내 곁에 없어.

TextEng: I am so sorry, but... I'm afraid that Evaine died while I was freeing her...
Text: 정말 미안하지만... 구하는 도중에 에바인이 죽었어...

TextEng: Yes, I've word. She's dead. Them's the breaks.
Text: 그래, 소식이 있어. 그녀는 죽었어. 어쩔 수 없었지.

TextEng: Not yet, but I'm working on it.
Yeah, yeah, I'll get around to it eventually.
Text: 알았어, 알았어. 언젠가는 하게 될 거야.

TextEng: Say where sister is again? Me forget.
Me find sister in Kurth's fortress... but she not here right now.
Text: 나 커스 요새에서 누이 찾았어... 근데 지금 여기 없어.

TextEng: Me so sorry... but she die when me try free her...
Text: 나 정말 미안... 근데 나 구하려다 그녀 죽었어...

TextEng: Me free sister, but she die on way. (belch!) Oh well.
Text: 나 누이 풀어줬는데, 오는 길에 죽었어. (꺽!) 뭐, 어쩔 수.

TextEng: No, but me working on it.
Me get around to it sometime, maybe.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Are you sure you can't? This is your sister, after all.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 정말 못 하는 거야? 네 여동생인데.

TextEng: Cough up some more gold, or I kill your sister now.
Text: 금화 더 내놔, 아니면 네 여동생 지금 죽여.

TextEng: That will be fine.
There's no need for the reward. You've lost enough.
Text: 보상은 필요 없어. 넌 이미 충분히 잃었으니까.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me thinks you could try. Sister important, no?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 너 할 수 있다고 생각해. 여동생 중요하잖아, 안 그래?

TextEng: No good. You gives more or me kills sister now.
Text: 안 돼. 돈 더 줘, 아니면 지금 누이 죽여.

TextEng: This is okay.
No, me no need gold. You loses enough.
Text: 아니, 나 금 필요 없어. 너 이미 많이 잃었어.

TextEng: Sorry, no, I'm not with <CUSTOM1071>.
Yes, I'm with <CUSTOM1071>.
Me not with <CUSTOM1071>, nope.
Yep - me with <CUSTOM1071>.
Maybe I could help, if you tell me what you're talking about.
Text: 무슨 얘기인지만 말해 준다면 도울 수도 있어.

TextEng: Me could help, if you say what me need do.
Text: 나 도울 수 있어, 나 뭐 해야 하는지 말해 주면.

TextEng: I've spoken to Kurth. He still has her and claims she is alive.
Text: 커스와 얘기했어. 아직 그녀를 데리고 있고 살아있다고 주장하더라.

TextEng: Me talks to Kurth. He say he gots her and she okay.
Text: 나 커스랑 말했어. 그가 그녀 잡고 있고 괜찮다 했어.

TextEng: I did what Kurth demanded... but he reneged on our deal.
Text: 난 커스가 요구한 대로 했는데... 놈이 약속을 저버렸어.

TextEng: Me do what Kurth want... but he still no let her go.
Text: 나 커스가 원하는 거 했어... 근데 아직도 그녀 안 놓아줘.

TextEng: She suffered plenty at Kurth's hands... and he has paid for it with his life.
Text: 그녀는 커스의 손에 많은 고통을 겪었어... 그리고 그는 그 대가로 목숨을 잃었어.

TextEng: She did not suffer, no... but Kurth is dead for what he did.
Text: 그녀는 고통받지 않았어... 하지만 커스는 자기가 한 짓 때문에 죽었어.

TextEng: She suffered, yes. Kurth remains alive, however.
Text: 그녀는 고통받았어. 하지만 커스는 아직 살아 있어.

TextEng: She did not suffer, no, and Kurth is not dead.
Text: 그녀가 고통받진 않았고, 커스도 죽지 않았어.

TextEng: Sister suffer, yeah... but Kurth be very dead for it.
Text: 누이 고생했어, 응... 근데 커스 아주 죽었어.

TextEng: Sister not suffer. Kurth be dead anyways.
Text: 누이 안 고생했어. 그래도 커스는 죽었어.

TextEng: Sister suffer, yeah. Kurth no dead, though.
Text: 누이 고생했어. 근데 커스는 안 죽었어.

TextEng: Sister no suffer. Me kills Kurth anyways.
Text: 누이 안 고생했어. 그래도 나 커스 죽였어.

TextEng: I don't think you want to know.
Me not think you wants to know.
Text: 나 생각해 너 알고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: She died screaming like a stuck pig, heh heh.
Text: 꼬챙이에 찔린 돼지처럼 비명 지르며 죽었지, 헤헤.

TextEng: She die screaming like stuck pig! Ha ha!
Text: 그녀 돼지처럼 소리 지르다 죽었어! 하하!

TextEng: Kurth has agreed to release Evaine if I do something for him.
Text: 커스가 부탁을 들어주면 에바인을 풀어 주겠다고 했어.

TextEng: Kurth wanted me to kill Baram, but I refused.
Text: 커스는 바람을 죽이라 했지만, 난 거절했어.

TextEng: Kurth say he give Evaine if me does something for him.
Text: 나 그 사람 부탁 들어주면 커스가 에바인 준다 했어.

TextEng: Kurth want me to kill Baram, but me say no.
Text: 커스가 바람 죽이라 했는데, 나 아니라고 했어.

TextEng: I'll try, Elynwyd.
Me try to, yeah.
I don't think so.
Me no think so.
Me gots news for you.... sister be dead.
Text: 나 너한테 소식 있어.... 여동생 죽었어.

TextEng: Actually, I have news for you... Evaine is dead.
